Compass Minerals International is a mineral supply company specializing in salt. The company's products include food salt, highway deicing salt, and water care products.
Information technology initiatives and operations for Compass Minerals International are led by the company's Chief Information Officer.

The department focuses on development of business applications and providing technical services for all IT infrastructure. A director oversees the application development group and… MoreInformation technology initiatives and operations for Compass Minerals International are led by the company's Chief Information Officer.

The department focuses on development of business applications and providing technical services for all IT infrastructure. A director oversees the application development group and leads a group of software developers working on applications like Oracle JD Edwards. Another director oversees the technical services group and is responsible for IT infrastructure including server management, systems engineering, and database operations.





