                	DriRox® 

                     Kiln-Dried Salt                




                    DriRox is a high performance deicing salt that every road maintenance program should have in its arsenal. Free-flowing and uniform in size, it delivers more effective and longer-lasting results because of lower moisture content than other solar salts.                




LEARN MORE






PRODUCT DESCRIPTION
 
Some salts have a moisture content of 2.0% or more, which can cause clumping, poor application, clogging and a variety of challenges. DriRox is kiln-dried solar salt with a moisture content less than 0.1%. This helps ensure:

No freezing or clumping
Better flow
More effective application
Faster acting than red salt
Easier mix to create brine













                	DUSTGARD® 

                     Treat Your Gravel Roads Better                




                    DustGard magnesium chloride is the preferred product for dust control, soil stabilization and wind erosion problems on roads and bare soil. 
                




LEARN MORE






PRODUCT DESCRIPTION
 
 
When applied to roads and bare soil areas, it immediately provides tangible benefits including:

Cleaner air, which leads to better health. Fugitive dust can cause health problems in the young, elderly and those with respiratory conditions.
Greater safety through improved road conditions, including increased driver visibility and decreased risks caused by loose gravel, soft spots, road roughness and flying rocks.
Stable soil, preventing destructive wind erosion. It reduces foreign sediment in nearby surface waters (dust that settles in creeks and streams), helps prevent stunted crop growth caused by clogged pores in plants and keeps vehicles and property cleaner.













                	FreezGard® 

                     The proven performer in the most challenging weather conditions                




                    Providing safe roads during the toughest winter storms requires more than an ordinary deicer. That's why we've created FreezGard, the leading high-performance anti-icing liquid on the market.  Transportation departments across the country trust FreezGard to create the safest roads with its unsurpassed low-temperature performance and superior melting capacity.                




LEARN MORE






PRODUCT LINE
 
FreezGard Lite
FreezGard Zero
FreezGard CI Plus
FreezGard Lite CI Plus












                	Gravel Roads Academy® 

                     Get Schooled In Gravelology                




                    Enroll in the Gravel Roads Academy and benefit from information and training on how to better maintain your gravel roads for superior stabilization, greater cost savings and better air quality.                 




LEARN MORE






PRODUCT DESCRIPTION
 
You don’t need to be a rocket scientist to know that the better a gravel road is made, the less it costs to maintain. Get your degree in Gravelology when the Gravel Roads Academy comes to a town near you. You’ll learn the latest techniques to creating and maintaining roads that help your budget go the extra mile.
 
Course Curriculum:

Road Design
Road Maintenance
Road Stabilization
Program Efficiency
Field Training













                	QwikSalt® 

                     Specially Enhanced To Quickly Clear Roads                




                    For an effective deicing solution that doesn’t sacrifice performance look to QwikSalt® – fast-acting, long-lasting and free of impurities. QwikSalt® is the budget-smart choice for your winter roads.                




LEARN MORE






PRODUCT DESCRIPTION
 
For years, salt has been the most cost-effective option to keep roads clear during harsh winter conditions. QwikSalt is the top choice for many reasons:

Over 99% pure sodium chloride
Mixed with magnesium chloride to enhance performance and storage
Blended with an anti-caking agent for optimal flowability
QwikSalt stays on the road, reducing bounce and scatter
Produced responsibly, using a solar evaporation process from the Great Salt Lake in Utah













                	Thawrox® 






                    Thawrox is the industry's premier deicing product, combining the performance of liquid deicing technology with proven melting effects of rock salt.                




LEARN MORE






PRODUCT DESCRIPTION
 
Using Thawrox means lower labor and equipment maintenance costs — so  deicing dollars go further than ever before. Quicker, longer and more effective performance using less salt.
 

Reduces bounce and scatter – 95% stays in the targeted application area
Good adhesion to roadway with continuing residual effects
Reduces fuel and labor costs
Works in cold temperatures (5˚F / -15˚C)
Less wind-borne loss of finer salt













                	SureSoft® 

                     Safe, Effective Performance For Family and Home® 




                    SureSoft is a 100% natural water softening solution. Effective in all traditional water softeners, our full line of water softening salts extends the life of appliances and fixtures, and makes homes operate more efficiently and effectively.                




LEARN MORE






PRODUCT LINE
 
Make a big impact on the quality of water, but a small impact on our planet – our bags contain 20% recycled materials and our products are 100% natural.
 
SureSoft® CubesPlus® with Resin Clean® 
SureSoft® CubesPlus® with Rust Buster® 
SureSoft® Extra Coarse
SureSoft® PelletsPlus® with Resin Clean® 
